        "TileImage": "$($repository 509e7448-a617-41a6-ad4a-bf9a08426914).Image",
        "Description": "Hello 47, your client today is Gary Lunn, a former mercenary and SIGMA operative. He has asked us to clear out the Sapienza Town Hall tower. Later tonight, a crew of 5 SIGMA ops will assassinate Salvatore Bravuomo and his assisstant, who reside in the Town Hall. He wants you to eliminate any guard or staff member who could get in the way and reveal the team&apos;s location.\rGood luck 47, and make it quick.",
